<td align="center"><b>
<i>Andrena mesoleuca</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Cockerell, 1924</font></b><br>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/mp/20q?search=Insecta">Insecta</a>
